LWP::Protocol::bbs is a simple extension to the LWP family that
allows retrieval of BBS objects from remote host running bbscomd.

Usage:

    % lwp-download bbs://elixus.org/boards/autrijus/articles/1/body

Where every slash ('/') denotes an element divisor.

Please refer to OurNet::BBS::PlClient and bbscomd for more information.
